After initially being granted an FDA Emergency Use Authorization (EUA) on May 1st, 2020,[L13236] remdesivir was fully approved by the FDA for the treatment of COVID-19 on October 22, 2020.[L18438] Remdesivir is currently marketed under the trademark name VEKLURY by Gilead Sciences Inc.[L18438] Remdesivir was also approved by the European Commission on July 3, 2020.[L39640] Remdesivir in combination with [baricitinib] for the treatment of COVID-19, was granted an FDA Emergency Use Authorization on November 19, 2020.[L22619]', '["J05AB16"]', '[]');
